[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "わあ……すごい人。\nさすがは国王陛下主催の大会だね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ジェロンたちも集まってるかな？\nみんな、どこ行ってるんだろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あれ？　なんだか見覚えのある人が……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ごきげんよう。遅かったですわね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鏑矢",
		"romanized_name": "Kaburaya",
		"model_path_hash": "2028850221954181122",
		"text": "このような催しがあるとはな。\n獣人限定でなければ、参加しているところであった！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3206719061125087729",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ララさんに、鏑矢さん！\nどうしてここに？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ジェロンが参加すると聞きまして、ひとつ激励をと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鏑矢",
		"romanized_name": "Kaburaya",
		"model_path_hash": "2028850221954181122",
		"text": "同じく、鬼門にはっぱをかけようと思っていた。\nあいつらのように",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3206719061125087729",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あいつら……？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アンペル",
		"romanized_name": "Empel",
		"model_path_hash": "6171220074376257282",
		"text": "お前なら負けることはないと思うが、無理はするな。\n己の力を存分に示してこい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2129139005935618031",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "リラ",
		"romanized_name": "Lila",
		"model_path_hash": "6420784340983749558",
		"text": "分かっている。\nアンペル、見ていろ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "658330190563200680",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユミア",
		"romanized_name": "Yumia",
		"model_path_hash": "8553801663070209956",
		"text": "レイニャ、大丈夫だよ。自分を信じて落ち着いて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3603268135404135156",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "レイニャ",
		"romanized_name": "Lenja",
		"model_path_hash": "5067796612903841500",
		"text": "は、はい……ユミアさん、ありがとうございます……\nレイニャ、頑張ります……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "326916344881311074",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "スレイ",
		"romanized_name": "Slade",
		"model_path_hash": "1119361770767559406",
		"text": "頑張れよ。ご馳走を作って待ってるからな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5581277904703418049",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "リアス",
		"romanized_name": "Rias",
		"model_path_hash": "8538886338969864227",
		"text": "ありがと！　あたし、全力でやってくるよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1321279492992502345",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "皆さん、来ていたんですね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "いったいどこから聞きつけたんだか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ん……ララ。なぜこんな所に",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "かつての仲間が戦うというのです。\n１つくらい言葉をかけてもいいでしょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたがたの勝利を信じていますわ。\n遠慮せず、思う存分やってきなさいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "フン。言われなくても",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "うん、頑張るよ！　ララさん、見ててね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鏑矢",
		"romanized_name": "Kaburaya",
		"model_path_hash": "2028850221954181122",
		"text": "鬼門、余の名に恥じぬ戦いを見せてこい！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3206719061125087729",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "これは鏑矢様！　\n鏑矢様のご期待、必ずや応えてみせまする！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "……みんな、大切な人の言葉を背負ってるんだ。\nアタシも負けてられないや",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "頑張って、イザナちゃん！\n一生懸命応援するからね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "うん、任せて！　\n絶対に最後まで残ってみせるから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "司会",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "さあ、皆さんお待たせいたしました！\n只今をもって、ベスティラ武道会を開始いたします！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "司会",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "観客の皆様は巻き込まれないよう\n観客席へと退避をお願いします！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "わあ！？　なんて豪快な始まり方！\nこれがベスティラ……！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "豪快って言うか、雑でしょ、こんなの！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "それじゃあ、行ってくるね！\n優勝もぎ取ってくるよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "それじゃあ、アタシたちも観客席に行こっか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "うん！　私たちの声援を、みんなに届けよう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]